game.instructions:
WASD \ Arrow Keys - move;
S \ Down Arrow - take\release an object;
CNTRL - interaction with objects: throw, hammer strike, invisibility mode;
SPACE - interaction with elevators and fuel stations;
Esc \ P - pause;

