game.instructions:
Move: Move Mouse; 
Shoot: Left Mouse; 
EMP: SPACE; 
Pause: P; 
Mute: M; 
Rotate building: SPACE;
Play the tutorial for more information!

There are 2 ways to change the pointer type35;8230;
1. Simply click the left mouse button until you get to the desired shape
2. Use the numbers 1 - 5 to accurately select the shape you would like to use (Recommended for later levels)

